OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FThe daughter of Black Sabbath frontman
OL,7,FOzzy Osbourne said she "aches every
OL,8,Fsingle day" and misses her father
OL,9,F"with every part of my soul" on the
OL,10,Ffirst anniversary of his death.
OL,12,FThe singer, from Birmingham, known as
OL,13,Fthe Prince of Darkness, died aged 76
OL,14,Fin July last year just over two weeks
OL,15,Fafter his Back To The Beginning
OL,16,Ffarewell concert where he was reunited
OL,17,Fwith his bandmates.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@KO]qD@AOUqD@\O]
