OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FHis youngest daughter, Kelly Osbourne,
OL,7,Fshared a lengthy and emotional tribute
OL,8,Fto Instagram on Wednesday addressed to
OL,9,Fher late father.
OL,11,FThe 41-year-old wrote: "One year ago
OL,12,Ftoday, the world changed forever.
OL,14,F"Today, I sit here beside you in a way
OL,15,FI never thought would be possible. I
OL,16,Fknow you are still with me.
OL,26,@sD@XOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784893683
OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,F"I feel you in the quiet, in the wind,
OL,7,Fin every song that stops me in my
OL,8,Ftracks, is (sic) the smell of your
OL,9,Fcologne and in every moment that love
OL,10,Foutweighs grief. You are all around
OL,11,Fme."
OL,13,FOsbourne detailed how living without
OL,14,Fher father "has been the hardest thing
OL,15,FI have ever had to endure" and said:
OL,16,F"Now all I have are memories.
OL,18,F"But my God, what beautiful memories
OL,19,Fthey are. Even through all the madness
OL,20,Fwe lived through, you somehow made
OL,21,Fevery moment worthwhile."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@DO]vD@LOUwD@ZO]xD@AOUzD@AOU}D@
OL,26,AYO]
