OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FThe TV star, who is also an actress,
OL,7,Frecounted fond memories with her
OL,8,Ffather and said: "I have never loved
OL,9,Fanyone or anything as deeply as
OL,10,Funiquely as I love you.
OL,12,F"And now I carry all of that love with
OL,13,Fnowhere to place it except within me,
OL,14,Fmy son, and mumma.
OL,16,F"It aches every single day, but it is
OL,17,Falso the greatest privilege of my
OL,18,Flife. To have loved someone so
OL,19,Fcompletely."
OL,26,@pD@ROUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@LO]
