OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FThe former Fashion Police star hailed
OL,7,Fthe impact Ozzy had on the world, and
OL,8,Fsaid: "You changed lives simply by
OL,9,Fbeing yourself and the beautiful
OL,10,Ftimeless music you created."
OL,12,FShe also praised her father's
OL,13,Fbackground, having come from a working-
OL,14,Fclass neighbourhood in Birmingham, and
OL,15,Fsaid he "never forgot what he came
OL,16,Ffrom".
OL,18,FOsbourne continued: "You made people
OL,19,Fbelieve that life could be better
OL,20,Fbecause of the way you lived yours.
OL,26,@pD@GOUrD@\O]wD@IOUxD@EO]zD@UOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784893683
OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,F"With honesty, loyalty, courage,
OL,7,Fhumour, and a heart bigger than anyone
OL,8,Frealised. There will never be another
OL,9,Fyou.
OL,11,F"You carried something extraordinary
OL,12,Finside you, a kind of magic that felt
OL,13,Fheaven-sent, and I will spend the rest
OL,14,Fof my life feeling grateful that I got
OL,15,Fto call you my daddy.
OL,17,F"This past year has broken me in ways
OL,18,FI never knew were possible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
