PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784893683
OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FOsbourne added: "Music may live
OL,7,Fforever, but what our family created
OL,8,Four bond, our laughter, our unwavering
OL,9,Flove is eternal. Death could never
OL,10,Ftake that from us."
OL,12,FThe star ended the emotional tribute
OL,13,Fby saying how much she loves and
OL,14,Fmisses Ozzy, whilst thanking him for
OL,15,F"being my daddy" and "making me who I
OL,16,Fam".
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@SO]wD@AOUwD@PO]wD@VOUxD@CO]
