OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FThe music star died of a reported
OL,7,Fheart attack on July 22 after
OL,8,Fsuffering a string of health issues
OL,9,Fover the years, including multiple
OL,10,Fsurgeries following a fall in February
OL,11,F2019 and being diagnosed with
OL,12,FParkinson's disease.
OL,14,FBlack Sabbath formed in 1968 and are
OL,15,Fwidely credited with defining and
OL,16,Fpopularising the sound of heavy metal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
