OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,FOsbourne also had a successful solo
OL,7,Fcareer and appeared in 2000s reality
OL,8,FTV series The Osbournes alongside his
OL,9,Fwife Sharon and their two youngest
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FOn the first anniversary of his death
OL,13,FOzzy was also remembered by his widow
OL,14,FSharon, who encouraged fans to
OL,15,F"remember how funny he was ` funny and
OL,16,Fcharismatic and real" in an interview
OL,17,Fwith BBC Radio West Midlands.
OL,19,FShe added: "He was authentic.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@UO]{D@LOU
