OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1784893683
OL,3,CDaughter of Ozzy Osbourne mourns her
OL,4,Cfather 'every day' a year after death
OL,6,F"He never tried to be anything other
OL,7,Fthan what he was, and he would tell
OL,8,Fyou the truth about everything and
OL,9,Fthat was him, you knew where you were
OL,10,Fwith him."
OL,12,FBilly Morrison, who is a guitarist for
OL,13,Frocker Billy Idol, also joined in the
OL,14,Ftributes, sharing a photo of himself
OL,15,Fwith his close friend and frequent
OL,16,Fcollaborator Ozzy to Instagram.
OL,18,FHe wrote: "I can't believe it's been a
OL,19,Fyear. I miss you mate."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]zD@KOU{D@WO]
